OL,2,MHave you thought about your digital
OL,4,Mlegacy?
OL,6,CIan Forrester
OL,7,CSun 10:00-10:20
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GDeath is inevitable, yet our digital
OL,11,Ginfrastructure remains woefully
OL,12,Gunprepared for it. While traditional
OL,13,G"Letters of Wishes" provide a static
OL,14,Groadmap for executors, they lack the
OL,15,Gagency to interact with our complex,
OL,16,Gdata-driven lives. This workshop
OL,17,Gintroduces the concept of the
OL,18,GMachine-Readable Letter of Wishes: a
OL,19,Gframework for post-mortem autonomy. By
OL,20,Gapplying a "If This, Then That"
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
